name: Cirupando and the smiling ones
description:
Cirupando
 | With a yellow bed and violet roofs
 | Of perfumed air and guardian of purity
 | Temple that does not admit pain
 | nor the memories that cause it

 | It leave the old world out
 | Cirupando is the capital of the rebooted
 | Of the smiling and white glowed
 | Of those who allow themselves to forget

 | Cirupando and his mirage
 | burn what weighs you down
 | what you won't let go
 | and you will walk clean among your brothers
 | in the new nature.

 | And you won't want to go back 
 | You won´t know anything else but peace
